<div class="title">Unexpected Knockdown</div>
<div class="substance">Alcohol - Beer & Alprazolam</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Bombenhagel&Exact=1">Bombenhagel</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Bombenhagel. "Unexpected Knockdown: An Experience with Alcohol - Beer & Alprazolam (exp60617)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Dec 5, 2007. erowid.org/exp/60617</div>

<br/>



